<title>mʿ sẖrwq ạlsẖms</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1-
 mʿ
 sẖrwq ạlsẖms mʿ lḥn ạlṭywr fy lwn ạlzhwr ạ̉sẖwf jmạl yswʿ
 ạlqrạr- ạ̉sẖwfk yạ yswʿ ạ̉sẖwfk bạlạ̹ymạn
 wạtẖq fyk msrwr ḥạss bạlạ̹mạn 2-
 mʿ
 gẖrwb ạlsẖms fy wqt ạlẓlạm lmạ ạlkwn ynạm ạ̉lms slạm yswʿ 3-
 lmạ
 ạ̉kwn frḥạn ạ̉htf bạllsạn
 ḥty̱ wạnạ zʿlạn
 ạ̉lms ḥnạn yswʿ</lyrics>
</song>